0:00:26,220 --> 0:00:29,330
承载在其他身体继续著旅行

10
0:00:35,280 --> 0:00:41,640
Eyes still closed,sunshine shone

11
0:00:41,890 --> 0:00:48,760
through the curtains of my eyes.

