You and I were closed at heart.

14
0:01:10,520 --> 0:01:17,060
Will you say that when we were apart?

15
0:01:17,340 --> 0:01:27,920
Time went too fast to feel your warmth and love.

16
0:01:28,910 --> 0:01:34,670
Never to warm my heart...

17
0:01:34,920 --> 0:01:42,440
Always beside you,that's all I wished for.

18
0:01:42,710 --> 0:01:48,480
Never to sad your heart...

19
0:01:48,770 --> 0:01:55,930
Can't bear losing my everything.

20
0:01:56,310 --> 0:01:59,230
感谢S1某前辈的友情出演

21
